---
const faqItems = [
  {
    question: "How quickly can I set up Agent for WhatsApp?",
    answer:
      "Most teams finish setup in around 5 minutes: install extension, connect model provider, run test connection, then enable trigger and persona settings.",
    link: "/blog/getting-started",
  },
  {
    question: "Which AI providers can I use?",
    answer:
      "You can connect OpenAI, OpenRouter, Groq, Gemini, and local models (for example Ollama/LM Studio). You can switch connectors anytime.",
    link: "/blog/getting-started",
  },
  {
    question: "What business workflows are included?",
    answer:
      "Toolbox includes lead management, batch sender, and scheduled messages. This gives you a practical pipeline for capture, follow-up, and conversion.",
    link: "/blog/advanced-guide",
  },
  {
    question: "Can we control reply behavior and safety?",
    answer:
      "Yes. You can define persona rules, trigger modes, private/group reply channels, limits, and quiet hours to keep automation predictable.",
    link: "/pricing",
  },
  {
    question: "How do Free, Pro, and Max differ?",
    answer:
      "Free is for basic setup and evaluation. Pro and Max unlock higher automation capacity, advanced controls, and stronger support for larger workloads.",
    link: "/pricing",
  },
  {
    question: "Can I measure whether it is working?",
    answer:
      "Yes. Dashboard shows WhatsApp connection state, bot status, and usage analytics like auto replies and recent trend, so performance is visible.",
    link: "/pricing",
  },
];
---

<section>
  <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-pink-600 font-semibold">FAQ</p>
    <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">Common Questions Before You Install</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-4">
    {
      faqItems.map((item) => (
        <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-[var(--line-soft)] bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none font-semibold text-gray-900 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
            <span>{item.question}</span>
            <span class="text-pink-600 group-open:rotate-45 transition">+</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">{item.answer}</p>
          <a href={item.link} class="mt-3 inline-block text-pink-600 font-medium hover:text-pink-700 underline">
            Learn more
          </a>
        </details>
      ))
    }
  </div>
</section>
